Utilizes dateStringEditor custom directive, which provides a text box with a date-picker button ({@link https://angular-ui.github.io/bootstrap/#/datepicker|ui-bootstrap})

@param {string} [format] - format string for date {@link https://docs.angularjs.org/api/ng/filter/date} 
  if not present, defaults to "MMMM dd, yyyy"
